      "description": "You control two drones at once. Every move command applies to both drones in lockstep. Park drone \"1\" on target \"a\" and drone \"2\" on target \"b\". Parked drones (\"A\"/\"B\") are locked in place. If a drone is blocked by a wall or the other drone, it now holds position while the other one can still move."
    },
