        "x----a---b--x",
        "x--x-----x--x",
        "x--1-----2--x",
        "x-----------x",
        "xxxxxxxxxxxxx"
      ],
      "description": "Timing matters more than distance. Use the shared controls to desynchronize both drones and then park them in order."
    },
    {
      "board": [
